Usage: db_browser [-help] <<obj_list>|head|top|selected>

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
<<obj_list>|head|top|selected>     # <<obj_list>|head|top|selected> 
                                   # head = root of the database for technology
                                   # information
                                   # top = top cell of the design
                                   # selected = set of selected objects
                                   # <obj_list> = list of object pointers.
                                   # (string, required)